Class EmptyHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cassite.pure.ioc.handlers.EmptyHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConstructorFilter, ParamAnnotationHandler, SetterAnnotationHandler, TypeAnnotationHandler

    public class EmptyHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements SetterAnnotationHandler, ParamAnnotationHandler, TypeAnnotationHandler, ConstructorFilter
    Handles every kind of annotations.
    false/null/exception would be returned/thrown in order to end the HandlingChain.
    priority Double.MAX_VALUE
